import './styles.scss' import Field_title from './Field_title'; const User = ({ name, id, username, email, phone, website, company: {name: companyName}, address: {street, suite, city, zipcode}}) => (

{name}

{id}

Username: {username};

Email: {email};

Phone: {phone};

Website: {website};

Company: {companyName};

Address: {street}, {suite}, {city}, {zipcode};

) export default User;
